	<h1 class="main">Where All Paths Lead to the Sea <sup>sm</sup></h1>
	<p>Nestled among the towering dunes along what has long been regarded as one of the most stunning stretches of coastline in Northwest Florida lies the WaterSound&reg; Beach community.  WaterSound Beach is a rare place that combines the spirit of community with the seclusion of a gated beachfront retreat in the heart of the Scenic Highway 30-A resort region and Florida's Emerald Coast. </p>
	<p>The community, which offers a variety of cottages, homes and upscale condominiums, embraces its natural surroundings.  Trails, pedestrian bridges and boardwalks link the various neighborhoods while gently meandering through the contours of the dunescape to the talcum white beach and the Gulf's emerald green waters. </p>
	<p><a href="/Amenities.asp">Community amenities</a> further enhance the resort-style living.  Each residence within the WaterSound Beach community has access to a distinctively designed swimming pool and gathering area. Landscaped parks and green spaces as well as a seasonal poolside restaurant foster a sense of camaraderie as well as an opportunity to enjoy the beautiful surroundings. </p>
